                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9122" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0982</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1221 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">树立国企品牌，争做低碳先锋： 渝隆环保的创新管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Establishing a State-Owned Enterprise Brand and Striving to Be a Low-Carbon Pioneer: The Innovation Management Path of Yulong  Environmental Protection</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘自敏，李兆耀，卿南京，张炜祥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆渝隆环保有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环境治理；企业社会责任；创新管理；可持续发展；2024百优案例；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Environmental governance, Corporate social responsibility, Innovation management, Sustainable developmen</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例研究对象重庆渝隆环保有限公司是一家从事环境咨询设计、环境治理及环保运营服务的国有企业。在国家“减污降碳协同增效”政策和“双碳”目标驱动下，渝隆环保积极履行企业社会责任，探索出一条经济效益、社会效益和生态效益协调发展的可持续经营道路。本案例以渝隆环保作为国有企业进行体制创新、创新管理为主线，回顾了公司在成立之初，面临行业竞争加剧、疫情冲击、撤资挑战等经营困境，通过内部变革，从组织、技术、模式三方面层层创新，最终实现企业可持续性发展并促进国有资产增值保值的实践历程。本案例旨在引导学生探讨在国内市场竞争加剧、混合所有制改革的背景下，国有企业改革创新的动因和方式，加深学生对相关知识点的理解和认识，启发学生对国有企业改革创新实践重要性的思考，也为同行业企业的创新发展提供参考与借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study examines Chongqing Yulong Environmental Protection Co., Ltd., a state-owned enterprise engaged in environmental consulting, governance, and operational services. Guided by the national policy of &quot;synergistic reduction of pollution and carbon emissions&quot; and the &quot;dual carbon&quot; goal, Yulong Environmental Protection has actively fulfilled its corporate social responsibility and explored a sustainable business that achieves a balance between economic, social, and ecological benefits. This case takes Yulong Environmental Protection as a state-owned enterprise to carry out system innovation and innovation management as the main line, and reviews the company&#39;s operating difficulties at the beginning of its establishment, such as intensifying industry competition, the impact of the COVID-19 epidemic, and capital withdrawal challenges. Through internal reforms, and innovation in its organizational structure, technology, and business models, Yulong Environmental Protection successfully realizes sustainable development and promotes the increment of state-owned assets value. This case aims to guide students to explore the motivations and methods of management innovation in state-owned enterprises under the background of intensified competition in the domestic market and mixed ownership reform, deepen students&#39; understanding and awareness of relevant knowledge points, inspire students to think about the importance of enterprise management innovation practice, and provide reference and inspiration for the innovation and development of enterprises in the same industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新管理价值实现；可持续发展；企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
